Team4450.Lib

Class Grip

  • java.lang.Object
    • Team4450.Lib.Grip

  • public final class Grip
extends java.lang.Object
    This class manages Grip run in a separate process. Starts/Stops that process and obtains Grip contour reports from that process via network tables.

      • getContoursReport

        public static Grip.ContoursReport getContoursReport()
        Gets current contours report from the data Grip posts to the network tables. Note that this data is about .75 seconds old, that is represents what the camera saw .75 seconds ago, not what the camera sees at the time this method is called.
        Returns:
        A ContoursReport object containing the list of contours (objects) found in the camera image. Grip should only return contours matching the target criteria.
